name: ACdb.tv
description: Add dynamic, auto-updating collections of movies and TV shows from ACdb.tv. Visit ACdb.tv for a quick overview.

versions.changelog: Support for Jellyfin version 10.11.0. This version of the plugin will not work with lower versions of Jellyfin. Use previous version if you have an older Jellyfin install.
Support for collections backdrops. Added better poster handling. Support for upcoming feature Library Posters. Support for upcoming optional feature to not send missing IMDB IDs.
